Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.27,0:00:04.06,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Something wasn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.75,0:00:07.94,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For some reason, that's how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:14.53,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}On TV, there was a match between two teams that I had never heard of before,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:18.15,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but for some odd reason, I felt compelled to cheer for the losing team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:22.55,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And, again for some odd reason, I had the feeling that Haruhi was about to cause a commotion again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:28.99,Haruhi,Imouto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kyon-kun, the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:30.48,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't have to tell me. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:35.48,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're free today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:37.77,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're all meeting in front of the station at exactly 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.05,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Make sure you come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.44,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't even get to say a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:45.34,Haruhi,Imouto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kyon-kun, the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:46.34,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:47.90,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:49.85,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I forgot to tell you what to bring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:52.77,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bring your swimming gear and lots of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:55.75,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Also, make sure you go there on a bike. Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:57.10,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:02.86,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have this feeling that I knew exactly what Haruhi was going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:05.90,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:10.03,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To be accurate, it feels more like the exact same thing has happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:12.42,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this what you call deja vu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:38.35,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're late, Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:39.74,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You need to show more enthusiasm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:40.93,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.35,0:01:42.83,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry for making you guys wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:44.87,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just got here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:48.16,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since everyone's here, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:48.83,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.92,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To the public pool, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.19,0:01:52.92,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I guess we would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:57.76,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since it's summer, we should have summer activities like what people do in the summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:01.01,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're never going to get back the time we lose, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:02.87,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why we're doing this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:05.99,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is our once-in-a-lifetime freshman summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:09.64,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By the way, we're going to the pool by bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.76,0:02:12.82,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You guys brought yours too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:15.73,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You and I are the only ones who brought bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:19.05,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:20.11,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How could I possibly be ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.49,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:24.59,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kyon, you can't lose to Koizumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:27.15,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now, commence take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:29.00,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:04.24,Haruhi Titles,{Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(500,420)}{\an8}Endless
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:04.24,Haruhi Titles,{Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(500,420)}Eight
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:05.64,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:08.39,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We came here to have fun, so what are you so unenthusiastic about anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:09.72,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're such a lazy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.98,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just whose fault is this anyway? Whose fault is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:19.05,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, the smell of chlorine! This is what it's all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.14,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, let's swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:23.36,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a race!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.54,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can't she see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.54,Haruhi Top,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sign: No Diving
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.55,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hurry up and get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:34.92,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The water is nice and warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:37.72,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It looks like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.23,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's quite a pleasant scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:45.25,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't you think Suzumiya-san may have found a normal way of enjoying things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:52.10,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seeing her having so much fun, there shouldn't be anything happening that will endanger the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:55.98,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If only that were true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.02,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:03.11,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Koizumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:07.66,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing. It's probably just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.67,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We've been through all sorts of things since spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.68,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think I might have become a little neurotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:15.40,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now, let's go swim as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:17.54,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.30,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:23.80,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:38.55,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Man, it'd be more appropriate to call this place a "pool for the masses" than a "pool for the public".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.14,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:51.24,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I feel like I've seen this somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:55.40,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For some reason, Nagato seems to be bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:56.28,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And then-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:56.83,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:06:01.00,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right. Then Haruhi said something like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.34,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}These two are my brigade members.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.71,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They'll listen to everything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.63,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So ask them anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:08.97,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, let's go have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.68,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're going to play water soccer! Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:14.33,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I guess deja vu happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:16.03,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here I come, Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:17.04,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.47,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.19,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:28.20,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I came up with an action plan for the rest of the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:32.63,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's our plan of how to spend what little remains of the summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:36.32,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are only two more weeks of summer vacation left, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:39.68,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It just feels like there's still so much to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:42.05,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In the end, we don't have any time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.84,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Got it? We're going all out from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:47.82,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mikuru-chan, do you have anything you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:51.67,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Umm, I would like to scoop up goldfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:55.71,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}OK. Goldfish scooping it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.35,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:02.30,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:07.09,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, I wonder if there's an Obon festival being held near here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.93,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A fireworks festival would be nice too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.94,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll go and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:13.47,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't forget the goldfish scooping!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:15.98,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Mikuru-chan's one passionate desire, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.12,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:20.87,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right Kyon, we start tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:27.80,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The next morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:32.18,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The call that stole away my indolence was, once again, from Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:37.71,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"We've found an Obon festival. Tonight at the public sports ground,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:38.62,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:43.31,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But Mikuru-chan and Yuki don't have yukatas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:46.53,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So now we're going to go buy yukatas for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:50.36,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't have one either, so I found a place that sells complete sets for a cheap price.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.10,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You come along too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:57.24,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haruhi led us into a bulk clothing store,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:08:00.01,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}personally chose Asahina-san and Nagato's yukatas,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:02.75,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and then immediately proceeded to drag them into the changing rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.90,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After making us wait for nearly an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.05,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fscx160}-{\fscx100} anyone would be yawning {\fscx160}-{\fscx100}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:07.54,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the three of them finally showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.59,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:13.26,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You girls look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:16.19,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course! I picked them out, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:17.62,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Especially Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:22.60,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's so cute! Just what I'd expect from myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.85,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.48,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Asahina-san, it's great! Asahina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.88,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There really is a lot of people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.53,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? I'm getting this feeling again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:43.52,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It should be my first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.52,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do I get the feeling that I've just been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:47.33,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:48.63,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That food stall...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.06,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:51.45,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:55.45,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They have the goldfish scooping that you wanted to do over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:56.97,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come here! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.15,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:01.12,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shall we do the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.39,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:16.16,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're interested in these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:22.27,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Which one do you want? I'll buy it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:22.73,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:24.48,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:25.41,Haruhi,Storekeeper,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:33.66,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For some odd reason, I feel like she's been looking after me, so paying for that would've been fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:39.00,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Man, we had a huge catch today! Huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:40.57,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thirteen fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:44.89,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But since we didn't need them all, we just kept one fish each.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:50.09,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, Yuki, what's with the mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:50.94,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:52.69,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.51,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me borrow your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.91,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, just turn the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:01.23,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:04.75,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay! Next is fireworks! Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.08,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's do that to finish today off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:10.84,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haven't you ever heard of the saying "Don't bite off more than you can chew"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:16.49,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When it's summer, there's summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:22.89,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So if I could have, I'd rather have forgotten about it, but there was one thing bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.49,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:29.56,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll go bug catching tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:32.40,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It will be the SOS Brigade Cicada Hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:38.20,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The person who catches the most will be Brigade Chief for one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.74,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haruhi, having fun is great and all, but have you finished your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:45.33,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:49.04,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Homework like that only takes three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:54.96,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Finish off all that tedious stuff so you can actually enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:58.37,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's the right way to enjoy summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:02.24,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why is this person so smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:07.96,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The next day, we got what you could call a ridiculously nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:12.34,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And on that day, we had the SOS Brigade Cicada Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:15.23,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone seemed to be putting up a fight but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:19.70,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For some familiar reason or another, the winner was Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:25.70,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The next day, we were gathered for some random reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:29.33,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}given a bunch of random frog costumes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:33.92,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and ended up handing out balloons in front of a supermarket as a small part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.91,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:39.31,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Man, I thought I was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:40.13,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Actually, I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.56,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks for your work everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.34,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You guys were great even in that heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.63,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The manager was really grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:48.02,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't need the old man's gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.02,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where's our pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:50.06,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:52.94,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've wanted this for a while now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:56.30,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks to Mikuru-chan, I was able to get the manager to give it to me as payment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:59.32,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You made us do all that work just for the sake of getting that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:02.82,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mikuru-chan, you can wear it whenever you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.30,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I give you permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.29,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:19.23,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My slumber was again stolen away by none other than a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:22.05,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:26.53,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.66,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kyon-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.19,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't tell me this is... Asahina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.69,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:41.77,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Something bad has...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.28,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If this goes on... I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:45.94,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:47.06,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hello. It's me, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:50.20,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you together with Asahina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:52.58,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A slight problem has occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.80,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you think you could come right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:55.82,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:56.67,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm on my way right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:19.05,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Asahina-san, what exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:20.63,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kyon-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:24.53,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't go back to the future anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:29.29,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can't go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:31.98,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um, "can't go back" as in...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:33.72,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In short, that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:38.17,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're currently looping through the same time period over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:40.13,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:43.76,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're currently looping through the same time period over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:47.32,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're currently looping-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:50.58,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, do you have any idea what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:51.77,Haruhi,Koizumi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:54.59,Haruhi,Koizumi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There is nothing more to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:56.89,Haruhi,Koizumi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was talking to Asahina-san just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:57.90,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Call me up too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:02.90,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As a result, I happened to notice that the flow of time has felt strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:06.08,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess you can say Asahina-san was the one that discovered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.78,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks to that, I was able to confirm something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.25,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Confirm what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:12.91,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're experiencing the same eternally repeating time period.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:17.23,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For a while now, it's been continuing to repeat over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:18.54,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You told me that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:23.82,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To be precise, the loop occurs from August 11th to August 31st.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:27.72,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're caged up in an endless summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.91,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah. "Caged up" would be the right term.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:34.09,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is an absolutely never ending, endless summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:39.35,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The world now has lost all time past September 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:42.90,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's the reason why Asahina-san is unable to return to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:47.32,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess it's only natural that you can't go back to a future that doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.15,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cut the crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:52.12,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What part of that nonsense is natural anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.04,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who the hell would believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:58.40,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was hoping that at least you would believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:04.23,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um, I'll give you an explanation too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:11.50,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I use *classified information* to communicate with the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:14.36,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and do things dealing with *classified information*.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:22.18,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For a week, I've had no *classified information*, so I thought: "That is strange..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:25.18,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And then *classified information*.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:27.78,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was really surprised,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.46,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so I did a *classified information*.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:33.12,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but it was completely *classified information*...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:35.12,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Asahina-san, are you just using the term "classified information" as a replacement for censoring words?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:44.31,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are we shut inside something similar to an enclosed space?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:45.66,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:48.88,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}One part of the time continuum has just been cut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:53.47,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When we reach August 31st, everything will be reset at exactly 2400 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:57.77,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and we will return to August 11th again. That's the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:01.27,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So what about our... no, the memories belonging to the entire human race?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:03.16,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That too gets reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:06.27,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everything starts over from the beginning again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:09.37,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And then time replays itself again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.88,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I get the feeling that this can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:16.87,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No. This one has nothing to do with Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:19.29,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So who's behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.50,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.39,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She might be unaware of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:30.78,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but a part of her might not want summer vacation to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.84,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Does she have some sort of regret?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:35.11,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:40.48,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It may very well be the fact that she feels like she still has something she needs to do during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:45.94,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Way to blow some meaningless, small issue into galactic proportions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:51.29,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was wondering but,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:53.48,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you're having fun, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:58.17,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've finally managed to solve the riddle of the deja vu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.88,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:03.74,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've come to understand that the imprints are the remains of a memory reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.75,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You've felt it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.62,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't tell me everyone in the world feels it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.28,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You and I are special cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:20.15,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just by being people who are close to Suzumiya-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:22.97,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}we've become the only people who are able to feel this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:24.40,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What about Haruhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:26.20,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't she at least aware of this herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:28.23,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It doesn't look like it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:32.00,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It would probably be a lot more complicated if she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.97,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's just that, with the deja vu,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:42.04,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm thinking that there must be someone who has retained all of his or her memories of the repeated time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.37,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And who would that someone be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:47.36,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think you'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:52.88,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nagato, is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:53.66,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:55.97,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you remember everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:56.59,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:02.10,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So how many times has that repeating thing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:06.40,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the fifteen thousand, four hundred and ninety-ninth time we have met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:10.85,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fifteen thousand, four hundred and ninety-ninth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:14.14,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you mean by 15,499?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:16.25,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nagato, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:20.71,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you being serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:21.69,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:26.64,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So for that number of times, did we do the exact same thing over and over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.31,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That is not necessarily the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:31.30,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In the last 15499 iterations,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.52,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}in regards to going to the Obon festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:37.63,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}we did not go 2,391 times and 11,054 times we went twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:43.16,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Also, Obon minus the goldfish scooping occurred 437 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:46.20,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Part-time work has been conducted a total of 9,026 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:48.33,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Within that, there have been six variations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.07,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Besides distributing balloons,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:53.66,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}we stocked shelves, worked as cashiers, distributed flyers, answered calls...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:55.61,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I get it, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:08.62,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}15,499 times. That's what Nagato said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:13.95,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Times the 2 weeks is... uhh, about 594 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:20.63,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Was she simply enduring all that time alone, living it over and over again while retaining her memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:26.77,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nagato, just how does it feel to have lived through all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:32.33,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard something ridiculous again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:36.65,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The next day was stargazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:38.86,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The venue was the rooftop of Nagato's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:42.02,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Koizumi prepared the telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:46.24,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:48.92,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's look for UFOs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:51.03,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haruhi, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:53.56,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey! Stop! It's going to break!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:01.72,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What exactly does she want to do, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:05.01,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now, I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.70,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Once we find that out, this problem will be relatively straightforward to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:11.07,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why don't we try this out for starters?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:14.23,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Suddenly hug Suzumiya-san from behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:17.07,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and whisper into her ear the words: "I love you".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.86,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And just who would be doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:21.24,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no one more suitable than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.03,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I exercise my right to veto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:26.64,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shall I do it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:32.69,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:34.54,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not qualified for that role.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:38.40,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I would only put Suzumiya-san into an unnecessary state of confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:45.25,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The queue of vigorous summer vacation events continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.03,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We went to the batting center...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:50.82,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And we went to a real fireworks show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:52.85,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We even took part in a fishing event.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:54.99,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Other activities included a test of courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:56.24,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}going to the theater,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:57.31,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}swimming in the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:58.51,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}bowling,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:20:59.97,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:02.55,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}None of us were exempted from singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:07.37,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course, I knew that this still wouldn't leave Haruhi satisfied,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:10.39,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so I didn't make any effort to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:14.42,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just like that, I ended up just passing through those days being miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:19.56,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Meanwhile, that critical day drew ever closer... August 31st.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.72,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With that we've pretty much completed our summer plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:32.30,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder if it's okay like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:36.02,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:38.94,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, do any of you want to do anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:44.68,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:48.41,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We've already done so much this summer, so it's probably enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.25,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No it's not, Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:53.98,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You aren't supposed to be satisfied yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:57.13,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, let's call it a day then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:22:01.28,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll let you have tomorrow off to prepare for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:03.46,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's meet in the clubroom in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.09,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Wait, Haruhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:10.76,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:11.56,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Deja vu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:14.68,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And this feels stronger than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:17.76,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't let Haruhi go home like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:18.89,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I let her go home,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.89,0:22:23.57,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}all those ten thousand something weeks will just end up being repeated again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:26.20,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:27.91,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:32.07,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There should be hints in Haruhi's words!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:33.50,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But what are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:36.46,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did she say until now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:39.54,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:42.34,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:00.94,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}August 31st.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:02.94,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Homework: unfinished.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.06,0:23:06.12,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't care anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:08.07,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It doesn't matter anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:16.65,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If everything really repeats again, doing this homework would be meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:26.63,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will tomorrow come or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:31.08,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I'll just have to leave it to myself to figure it out later.
